@page "/Career"

<div class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size: 5rem;">A CAREER AT KELBURG</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-curve">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path fill="#fff" d="M0,320C480,320,960,0,1440,0V320H0Z"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-bold">AT KELBURG WE LIKE TO DO THINGS DIFFERENTLY</h4>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>
                Welcome to <strong>Kelburg Hotel</strong>, where luxury meets innovation – and where <strong>you pay us</strong> for the <em>privilege</em> of working here.
            </p>
            <p>
                Regular jobs? He– Hell naw. Overrated. We offer an <strong>exclusive</strong> opportunity to gain <em>invaluable</em> experience by working at Kelburg. You also gain the benefit of bragging about how you work at the most prestigious hotel in the world. Now that's payment enough!
            </p>

            <div class="mt-4">
                <strong>What You Get (By Paying Us):</strong>
                <ul class="mt-2">
                    <li><strong>The honor</strong> of serving our esteemed guests.</li>
                    <li>A <strong>once-in-a-lifetime</strong> opportunity to learn the secrets of 8-star hospitality.</li>
                    <li>A chance to <strong>prove your dedication</strong> – Nothing says commitment like investing in your own job!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center my-5">
                <button class="btn btn-warning btn-lg px-5 rounded-pill fw-bold" style="background-color: #C9A66B; border-color: #C9A66B">APPLY</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="mt-5" />

    <footer class="text-center text-muted py-4">
        <div>
            <img src="images/logo.png" alt="Kelburg Hotel Logo" style="width:120px;" class="mb-2"/>
            <div><small>From Historic Charm to Modern Luxury</small></div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>